				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mu _{x}$$\end{document} is the chemical potential of species x. For a reductive process, the Gibbs free energy G can be related to the electrode potential U as10ΔG=-eU\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
